        <section id="intro">
            <page_title>
                <title>Dungeon Denizens</title>
                <title>Beholderkin Bestiary</title>
            </page_title>
            <p space="8">
                Beholderkin is a family of aberrations normally found in the deep underworld or in the Nether.
                They range in size, color, number of eye stalks, and magic ability. There are four known beholderkin -
                Beholders, Death Tyrants, Gazers and Spectators.
            </p>
        </section>
        <section id="beholder">
            <title>Beholder</title>
            <p>Blurb about beholder goes here...</p>
            <p>Number: 1</p>
            <p>Size: Large</p>
            <p>Level: Mini Boss</p>
            <p>Rarity: Rare</p>
            <p>Movement: Flies/Hovers (~20ft / 7 blocks)</p>
            <p>Speed: Normal</p>
            <p>Health: 36hp</p>
            <p>Damage/Strength: 8hp</p>
            <p>Daylight: Yes</p>
            <p>Despawn: Yes</p>
            <p>Spawns: Underworld, Nether</p>
            <p italics="true">Weapons/Specials:</p>
            <p indent="4">- Randomly casts one of four spells: Paralysis, Harm, Disintegrate and Disarm.</p>
            <p indent="4">- Can summon one minion at a time: Headless, Orc, Spectator, or Blaze.</p>
            <p indent="4">- Every 2 minutes, has a 10% chance to summon a Daemon.</p>
        </section>
        <section id="Death Tyrant ">
            <title>Death Tyrant</title>
            <p>A Death Tyrant is an undead Beholder that has retained some of its magical abilities, mainly the ability to summon minions.</p>
            <p>Number: 1</p>
            <p>Size: Large</p>
            <p>Level: Mini Boss</p>
            <p>Rarity: Rare</p>
            <p>Movement: Flies/Hovers (~24ft / 8 blocks)</p>
            <p>Speed: Normal</p>
            <p>Health: 36hp</p>
            <p>Damage/Strength: 8hp</p>
            <p>Daylight: Yes</p>
            <p>Despawn: Yes</p>
            <p>Spawns: Underworld, Nether</p>
            <p italics="true">Weapons/Specials:</p>
            <p indent="4">- Can cast Paralysis spell.</p>
            <p indent="4">- Can summon multiple minions at once including Zombies, Husks and Skeletons.</p>
        </section>
    </chapter>
